Frontend Framework & Build Tools:
React (v18.3.1) - JavaScript library for building user interfaces
TypeScript - Type-safe JavaScript development
Vite - Fast build tool and development server

Styling & UI:
Tailwind CSS - Utility-first CSS framework for styling
shadcn/ui - Pre-built component library built on top of Radix UI
Radix UI - Headless UI components for accessibility
Lucide React - Icon library for consistent iconography

State Management & Data Fetching:
React Query (@tanstack/react-query) - Server state management
React Hook Form - Form handling and validation
Zod - Schema validation

Routing & Navigation:
React Router DOM - Client-side routing

Additional Libraries:
date-fns - Date utility library
Recharts - Chart and data visualization library
Sonner - Toast notifications
class-variance-authority & clsx - Conditional CSS class utilities

Development Tools:
ESLint - Code linting
PostCSS - CSS processing
Tailwind CSS Animate - Animation utilities
This tech stack provides a modern, performant, and maintainable foundation for building professional portfolios with excellent user experience and developer experience.

